text: Sahina Mumtaz Begum is an Indian politician. In 2019 she is elected as MLA of Naoda Vidhan Sabha Constituency in West Bengal Legislative Assembly.List of Winners in West Bengal 2016 She is an All India Trinamool Congress politician. She is Nasiruddin Khan's daughter-in-law. ==References== Category:Living people Category:All India Trinamool Congress politicians Category:Bengali politicians Category:Women in West Bengal politics Category:Members of the West Bengal Legislative Assembly Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
